# Root-level example env file.
# Per-service environment variables live next to their compose files,
# e.g. services/nextcloud/.env.example.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` only if a root-level tool (Terraform/Ansible/etc.)
# needs shared variables. Real `.env` files are ignored by git.

# Example shared values (uncomment when actually used):
# TZ=Europe/Warsaw
# DOMAIN_INTERNAL=home
# LAN_CIDR=192.168.1.0/24
